Meet our Team
Beth Ann Lee, Community Manager
Beth Ann Lee moved from Maine to Florida several years ago because shoveling sunshine is easier than snow. She is very involved in church, and loves the beach, traveling, reading, and playing golf. She also enjoys spending time with her 3 boys and her grandkids. We are very happy to have her as part of our Rickert Properties team! We invite you to visit Silver Oaks & Oak Gardens to meet the residents and tour our Models and preloved homes for sale. You will see why these are the communities you will want to call home here in sunny Florida!
Jodi Susco, Regional Operations Manager
Jodi Susco the Regional Operations Manager is originally from Minnesota and has been with Rickert Properties for over 18 years. Jodi loves to read books, spend time with family & friends and cares for the resident’s furry friends by carrying treats in her golf cart! We are happy to have Jodi aboard our Rickert Properties team as she does an exceptional job in keeping the community looking fantastic.
